2
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:09,800
Wait, this is good.

3
00:02:10,700 --> 00:02:11,900
I did it!

4
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:16,800
I infiltrated this place!

5
00:02:17,900 --> 00:02:19,200
Success!

6
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,500
大作戦！
The big mission!

7
00:02:23,700 --> 00:02:26,300
あ、みんなに見られた！
Ah, everyone saw me!

8
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:29,400
I can't believe you guys were watching me

9
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,900
this whole time! No!

10
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:36,700
To be honest, I did feel... I did feel eyes on me,

11
00:02:36,700 --> 00:02:41,200
but I knew you guys were watching, it's okay.

12
00:02:42,100 --> 00:02:44,800
Anyways, it's not the time to be talking

13
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,000
about that because

14
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:51,500
today is a special day for me! Whee! Yeah!

15
00:02:53,300 --> 00:02:55,300
Do you know what today is?

16
00:02:55,300 --> 00:02:57,400
Say it, say it! Say it, say it!

17
00:02:57,400 --> 00:03:00,000
Yeah, today is my birthday!

18
00:03:04,100 --> 00:03:08,500
Happy birthday Zeta, happy birthday Zeta,

19
00:03:08,500 --> 00:03:11,000
Selamat ulang tahun Zeta.
Happy birthday, Zeta.

20
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,500
こんな感じだっけ？
Is that how it goes?

21
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:15,800
I don't know. Well...

22
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:18,000
Oh, what? You're saying something? Huh?

23
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:22,000
Mmm, nope.

24
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,800
Skill issue!

25
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:28,900
You're saying I'm a noob as a secret agent?

26
00:03:29,500 --> 00:03:32,400
Bulls... Okay, I can't say the rest. Bulls.

27
00:03:32,500 --> 00:03:34,900
Your lies, you're lying! That can't be true.

28
00:03:35,300 --> 00:03:39,000
I've been working hard. I've got the stamina,

29
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:42,000
and obviously the intelligence,

30
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:44,200
IQ 二百！
IQ 200!

31
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:46,000
And strength, you know?

32
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:48,300
Got the power as well. Yeah, yeah, yeah.

33
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:54,400
So anyways, don't you worry because

34
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:57,000
I've got the perfect thing for today.

35
00:03:57,000 --> 00:04:00,000
Yeah, yeah, yeah. Have you ever heard of a...

36
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:03,000
of a secret agent school?

37
00:04:03,500 --> 00:04:06,500
Yeah, so... back in my days, back in my days,

38
00:04:06,500 --> 00:04:09,500
I've been through hell and back,

39
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:13,000
so I invited some tests for students here

40
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:15,500
so we can prove that I'm the best secret agent, okay?

41
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:19,000
So, we're going to do some tests together to see

42
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:22,000
how tough it is to become a professional

43
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:24,000
secret agent like me, like me, like me!

44
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,000
I'm a good example.

45
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:28,000
Anyways, it reminds me of my old gakko-ism,
Anyways, it reminds me of my old school days,

46
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:30,500
you know? But to be honest, to be honest...

47
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:35,500
To be honest, I don't know what we'll be doing yet, but...

48
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,500
Wait, oh crap! Okay,

49
00:04:39,500 --> 00:04:40,800
it's almost time for the first test!

50
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:43,100
最初のテストか... そろそろ...
Is it the first test? Soon...

51
00:04:43,300 --> 00:04:45,500
あ！早く行かないと！
Ah! I have to go fast!

52
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:47,800
Bye!

53
00:04:55,300 --> 00:04:57,000
来るなー！
Don't come!

54
00:05:02,288 --> 00:05:03,888
なんかさ...
Hey...

55
00:05:09,988 --> 00:05:11,388
あれ？なんか...
Wait, something...

56
00:05:12,088 --> 00:05:15,088
みこちのカマキリの威嚇ポーズにビビってる。
It's scared of Miko-chi's praying mantis intimidation pose.

57
00:05:15,988 --> 00:05:18,288
ビビってる、ビビってる。プルプル。
It's shaking with fear.

58
00:05:19,388 --> 00:05:20,988
これみこちゃんわかりました。
I've got it.

59
00:05:20,988 --> 00:05:23,388
コイツ雑魚ゾンビです。
This guy is a weakling zombie.

60
00:05:24,588 --> 00:05:26,088
ざぁ～こ
Nooooob.

61
00:05:26,088 --> 00:05:28,388
ざぁ～こ
Nooooob.

62
00:05:28,988 --> 00:05:31,088
コイツどMかも知れん。
He might be a major masochist.

63
00:05:31,088 --> 00:05:33,288
どMゾンビかも。
Maybe a masochist zombie.

64
00:05:35,588 --> 00:05:37,288
ポンコツ～
Useless~

65
00:05:39,088 --> 00:05:40,988
もしかして... じゃみこちゃんも言っていい？
Perhaps... Can I say it too?

66
00:05:40,988 --> 00:05:42,388
みこちゃんも言って。
You go ahead and say it too.

67
00:05:42,388 --> 00:05:44,488
ざぁ～こ
Nooooob.

68
00:05:46,988 --> 00:05:49,088
ちょっとヨワヨワゾンビさんなんじゃない？
Isn't he a bit of a weakling zombie?

69
00:05:49,088 --> 00:05:52,288
なんじゃないですか？全然怖くないんですけど。
Isn't he? I'm not scared at all though.

70
00:05:52,288 --> 00:05:55,488
ヨワヨワ～
So weak~

71
00:05:57,988 --> 00:05:59,588
あー、みんな！
Ah, everyone!

72
00:06:00,988 --> 00:06:05,388
遅れてごめーん！
Sorry I'm late!

73
00:06:06,988 --> 00:06:08,388
なにこのゾンビ？
What is this zombie?

74
00:06:08,988 --> 00:06:12,088
あれはヨワヨワゾンビ。
That's a weakling zombie.

75
00:06:12,988 --> 00:06:17,088
エージェントスクールの最初のテストにお招きしたけど、
I invited you for the first test of the Agent School,

76
00:06:17,088 --> 00:06:20,288
ゾンビも新入生なのかな？
but I wonder if the zombie is also a new student?

77
00:06:20,288 --> 00:06:22,088
新入生？！
A new student?!

78
00:06:25,988 --> 00:06:30,088
そうだ、でも言葉通じないけどさ、ゾンビに。
Right, but we can't communicate with the zombie.

79
00:06:30,088 --> 00:06:33,388
ゼータは言葉いろんな言葉話せるよね。
Zeta, you can speak many different languages, right?

80
00:06:34,088 --> 00:06:37,388
ゾンビ語もしゃべれるんじゃないの？
Can't you speak Zombie-ish too?

81
00:06:37,388 --> 00:06:39,088
えー！ちょっと待って、待って。
Wait, wait a minute.

82
00:06:39,088 --> 00:06:41,388
オッケー、オッケー。
Okay, okay.

83
00:06:45,988 --> 00:06:47,988
ちょっと弱そうかも。
He seems a bit weak.

84
00:06:47,988 --> 00:06:52,288
会話してる！
They're having a conversation!

85
00:06:53,088 --> 00:06:54,988
よし、できた。
Alright, I did it.

86
00:06:54,988 --> 00:06:56,088
できた？！
You did it?!

87
00:06:56,488 --> 00:06:58,288
おい！ゾンビ！
Hey! Zombie!

88
00:06:58,988 --> 00:07:00,288
何してるの！
What are you doing?!

89
00:07:00,288 --> 00:07:02,288
怖がらせろって言ったでしょ？！
I told you to be scary, didn't I?!

90
00:07:02,988 --> 00:07:05,988
ほんとに何やってたのよ！
What have you been doing?!

91
00:07:07,088 --> 00:07:09,288
ごめんあそばせ。
Apologies.

92
00:07:09,288 --> 00:07:11,388
どうやら弱っちいゾンビを送っちゃったみたいね。
I probably sent over the weak zombies.

93
00:07:11,388 --> 00:07:13,288
申し訳ないわね。
Sorry about that.

94
00:07:13,288 --> 00:07:17,088
さて、今日はみなさんにサプライズテストをご用意しました。
Anyways, I called you guys here for a surprise test.

95
00:07:17,088 --> 00:07:21,488
シークレットエージェントにふさわしいか、確かめてみましょう。
To see if you guys are fit to be a secret agent.

96
00:07:23,388 --> 00:07:25,288
なんか分かんないけど受ける。
I don't really get it, but I'll take it.

97
00:07:25,288 --> 00:07:27,388
なんか分かんないけど受けてみるか。
Should we try taking it?

98
00:07:27,388 --> 00:07:29,288
受けてみよう。
Let's try.

99
00:07:29,988 --> 00:07:32,388
さてさて、みなさん落ち着いてくださいね。
Okay, okay, calm down everyone.

100
00:07:32,988 --> 00:07:38,288
では、この箱の中身を当ててもらうテストになります！
In this test, you will need to guess what is inside the box!

101
00:07:38,288 --> 00:07:40,988
箱の中身！
Guess what's inside!

102
00:07:41,488 --> 00:07:47,388
ラウンド1では、30秒だけ中身に触れられます。
For round 1, you can feel the object for 30 seconds only.

103
00:07:47,988 --> 00:07:49,488
楽しんでくださいね。
Have fun.

104
00:07:49,988 --> 00:07:54,288
みなさんのリアクション、すっごく楽しみですね。
Can't wait to see your reactions.

105
00:07:54,988 --> 00:07:57,088
いいリアクション期待してるよだって。
She says she's expecting good reactions.

106
00:07:57,088 --> 00:07:59,288
完全に馬鹿にしてるから。
She's totally making fun of us.

107
00:08:00,988 --> 00:08:02,988
当たり前じゃん。
Of course she is.

108
00:08:02,988 --> 00:08:05,388
じゃあAZKi先輩からかな？
Will we start with AZKi-senpai?

109
00:08:07,988 --> 00:08:10,088
任せてくださいよ。
Please leave it to me.

110
00:08:10,088 --> 00:08:13,288
これはさ、みんなで協力してだよね。
We should all cooperate on this, right?

111
00:08:15,988 --> 00:08:20,288
伝えることに集中したいと思います。
I'll focus on communicating what I feel.

112
00:08:20,988 --> 00:08:23,388
AZKiの挑戦
AZKi's Challenge

113
00:08:23,988 --> 00:08:26,388
Three, two, one, start!

114
00:08:26,988 --> 00:08:29,388
うわ！え？これ？
Whoa! Wait, this?

115
00:08:31,988 --> 00:08:34,288
えっと、コードのような...
Um, it's like a cord...

116
00:08:34,288 --> 00:08:36,288
コード？
A cord?

117
00:08:36,988 --> 00:08:38,388
ちょっと待って、なにこれ！
Wait a minute, what is this!

118
00:08:38,388 --> 00:08:42,388
Frog toy

119
00:08:42,988 --> 00:08:46,288
なんかじたばたしてます、じたばた。
It's flailing around, flailing.

120
00:08:46,288 --> 00:08:48,388
じたばた？動いてる！
Flailing? It's moving!

121
00:08:53,988 --> 00:08:56,388
え、なんか動いている...けど...！
Eh, it's moving... but...!

122
00:08:56,988 --> 00:08:58,388
Time's up!

123
00:09:00,988 --> 00:09:02,988
フォルムがわからない。
I can't tell the shape.

124
00:09:03,988 --> 00:09:06,288
なんか足がバタバタしてるみたい。
It felt like legs were kicking.

125
00:09:06,988 --> 00:09:11,388
バタバタ？えー！
Kicking? Whoa!

126
00:09:11,988 --> 00:09:14,388
大神ミオの挑戦
Ookami Mio's Challenge

127
00:09:14,988 --> 00:09:17,388
じゃ、ミオしゃ、start!
Then, Mio-sha, start!

128
00:09:26,988 --> 00:09:30,288
あ！あ！何か気づいた。
Ah! I noticed something.

129
00:09:30,988 --> 00:09:33,388
でも分かったかもこれうち。
But I think I might have figured it out.

130
00:09:34,988 --> 00:09:39,388
あー、はいはいはい...
Ah, yes yes yes...

131
00:09:39,988 --> 00:09:42,388
あー、元気ですね。
Ah, it's very energetic.

132
00:09:46,988 --> 00:09:49,088
完全に生きてますよ。
It's definitely alive.

133
00:09:49,088 --> 00:09:50,288
Time's up!

134
00:09:50,288 --> 00:09:52,388
あー元気だったな、すごい元気だった。
Ah, it was energetic, really energetic.

135
00:09:53,988 --> 00:09:56,388
絶対生きてるんだ。
It's definitely alive.

136
00:09:57,988 --> 00:10:00,388
さくらみこの挑戦
Sakura Miko's Challenge

137
00:10:00,569 --> 00:10:01,769
ゴッドハンドみこ
God Hand Miko...

138
00:10:01,769 --> 00:10:02,869
ゴッドハンドみこです！
...God Hand Miko is here!

139
00:10:02,969 --> 00:10:03,769
頑張って！
Do your best!

140
00:10:03,769 --> 00:10:05,069
3, 2, 1...

141
00:10:05,069 --> 00:10:05,669
Go!

142
00:10:05,669 --> 00:10:07,069
え、虫絶対やだ
Wait, I definitely don't want bugs.

143
00:10:07,669 --> 00:10:09,669
ギャーーー！
AAAHHH!

144
00:10:14,069 --> 00:10:16,069
何かに触れた模様
Looks like she touched something.

145
00:10:16,669 --> 00:10:17,569
ギャーーー！
AAAHHH!

146
00:10:18,669 --> 00:10:19,969
やめて、マジですか？
Stop it, are you serious?

147
00:10:22,069 --> 00:10:24,069
ガチなやつ、ガチなやつ
This is for real, this is for real.

148
00:10:27,069 --> 00:10:28,669
ねぇ、やめて！
Hey, stop it!

149
00:10:31,369 --> 00:10:32,869
真剣な表情
A serious expression.

150
00:10:33,669 --> 00:10:34,569
わかった？
Did you figure it out?

151
00:10:34,569 --> 00:10:36,069
全然わかんない
I have no idea.

152
00:10:36,669 --> 00:10:37,869
Time's up!

153
00:10:37,869 --> 00:10:39,369
全然わかんない
I have no idea.

154
00:10:39,369 --> 00:10:40,569
終わりだよ
It's over.

155
00:10:41,569 --> 00:10:43,069
え、ゴッドハンド？
Eh, God Hand?

156
00:10:43,069 --> 00:10:44,769
ゴッドハンド？
God Hand?

157
00:10:44,769 --> 00:10:46,569
ブルルッてなって
It went "brrrr"...

158
00:10:46,569 --> 00:10:47,869
めっちゃきもい！
It was so gross!

159
00:10:49,669 --> 00:10:51,069
じゃあ次はゼータ！
Alright, next is Zeta!

160
00:10:51,069 --> 00:10:53,069
じゃあ次はゼータ、行け！
Alright, next is Zeta, go!

161
00:10:54,169 --> 00:10:57,069
ベスティア・ゼータの挑戦
Bestia Zeta's Challenge

162
00:10:57,769 --> 00:10:58,769
行きますよ
Here I go.

163
00:10:58,769 --> 00:10:59,569
行きます！
Going!

164
00:10:59,669 --> 00:11:00,869
3, 2, 1...

165
00:11:00,869 --> 00:11:01,869
Start!

166
00:11:02,669 --> 00:11:04,069
うわ、何これ？
Whoa, what's this?

167
00:11:06,069 --> 00:11:08,069
え、これ生きてるやん
Eh, this is alive.

168
00:11:09,869 --> 00:11:12,369
多分生きてない気がするけど
I have a feeling it's probably not alive, but...

169
00:11:14,869 --> 00:11:17,369
え、何これ？
Eh, what is this?

170
00:11:17,869 --> 00:11:20,069
今、結構触っています
She's touching it quite a bit now.

171
00:11:20,669 --> 00:11:22,369
何これ？
What is this?

172
00:11:23,569 --> 00:11:24,569
え、飛んでる？
Eh, is it flying?

173
00:11:24,569 --> 00:11:26,669
これ飛んでる？
Is this flying?

174
00:11:26,869 --> 00:11:28,669
なんか飛びそうではあるよね
It does look like it's about to fly.

175
00:11:28,669 --> 00:11:30,569
飛びそうだよね
It looks like it might fly.

176
00:11:31,069 --> 00:11:32,569
飛びそう
Looks like it'll fly...

177
00:11:32,669 --> 00:11:33,869
生きてる…！
It's alive...!

178
00:11:33,869 --> 00:11:35,069
Time's up!

179
00:11:35,069 --> 00:11:36,669
生きているのかなんなのか
Is it alive or what?

180
00:11:37,069 --> 00:11:38,769
いやー、これちょっと
Man, this is a bit...

181
00:11:40,869 --> 00:11:42,669
でもこれみんなでね
But everyone, together...

182
00:11:42,669 --> 00:11:44,769
力を合わせて
...combine our strength.

183
00:11:44,769 --> 00:11:46,569
誰か一人でも当てればってことで
As long as at least one of us gets it.

184
00:11:47,069 --> 00:11:48,869
プロペラがついたもの？
Something with a propeller?

185
00:11:48,869 --> 00:11:50,569
何か付いてたのかなって
I wondered if something was attached.

186
00:11:52,069 --> 00:11:53,569
マジでみこが手を入れた時に
Seriously, when Miko put her hand in...

187
00:11:53,569 --> 00:11:55,869
ブルルッてなったから
...it went "brrrr"!

188
00:11:56,869 --> 00:11:58,769
アヒルの玩具
A duck toy

189
00:11:56,869 --> 00:11:58,769
アヒルとかの足がこう
Like the feet of a duck...

190
00:11:58,769 --> 00:12:00,569
バタバタバタってなってる
...going flap flap flap.

191
00:12:00,569 --> 00:12:02,669
バタバタバタみたいな
Like "batabata"...

192
00:12:02,669 --> 00:12:04,569
なんかそういうおもちゃ
Some kind of toy like that.

193
00:12:04,569 --> 00:12:05,669
ミオ先輩は？
How about Mio-senpai?

194
00:12:05,669 --> 00:12:07,569
これはズバリ
This is, without a doubt...

195
00:12:07,569 --> 00:12:09,069
カエルの玩具
A frog toy

196
00:12:07,569 --> 00:12:09,069
カエルの玩具です
...a frog toy.

197
00:12:09,069 --> 00:12:10,669
ぴょこぴょこ
Hop hop hop.

198
00:12:10,669 --> 00:12:12,669
ブルブルしてたってこと？
So it was vibrating?

