890
00:47:39,139 --> 00:47:42,139
やー！適当に打つ！
Ya! I'll just shoot randomly!

891
00:47:43,139 --> 00:47:45,139
あ、でも惜しい惜しい！
Ah, but that was close, close!

892
00:47:45,139 --> 00:47:47,139
がんばれ、がんばれ...
Good luck, good luck...

893
