Alright, let's go, Laplus! Here we go!

928
00:49:41,139 --> 00:49:43,639
3、2、1、スタート！
3, 2, 1, Start!

929
00:49:44,139 --> 00:49:46,139
このゲームには必勝法がある！
There's a winning strategy to this game!

930
00:49:46,139 --> 00:49:47,639
めっちゃ回っとるやん！
She's spinning a lot!

931
00:49:53,139 --> 00:49:55,139
後ろから撃ってるのヤバいって！
Shooting from behind is crazy!

932
00:49:55,139 --> 00:49:57,139
当たってないよ！
You're not hitting!

933
00:49:59,139 --> 00:50:01,139
当たってないよ！
You're not hitting!

934
