942
00:50:18,927 --> 00:50:19,927
絶対行きたい！
I definitely want to go!

943
00:50:19,927 --> 00:50:20,927
絶対行きたい？
You definitely want to go?

944
00:50:20,927 --> 00:50:21,927
あ、行きたい行きたい！
Ah, I want to go, I want to go!

945
00:50:32,227 --> 00:50:34,427
メーター調整行きましょう！
Let's go with the meter adjustment!

946
00:50:34,627 --> 00:50:37,927
3, 2, 1, Go!

947
00:50:38,427 --> 00:50:39,427
Start!

948
