回ってるんだけど、私が
I'm the one who's spinning.

949
00:50:49,927 --> 00:50:51,427
ゼータちゃんも回ってる
Zeta-chan is spinning too.

950
00:50:56,627 --> 00:50:58,427
あと...あと12秒
12... 12 seconds left.

951
00:50:58,427 --> 00:50:59,927
裏面だったなー今の
That was the back side just now.

952
00:51:04,927 --> 00:51:06,427
これはもう後ろから！
This has to be from behind!

953
00:51:09,427 --> 00:51:10,927
Time's up!

954
00:51:13,927 --> 00:51:15,927
ゼータ、すごいヒーローです
Zeta, you're a great hero.

955
00:51:16,927 --> 00:51:18,427
これむずいよ
This is so hard.

956
00:51:24,927 --> 00:51:27,927
最後やからまつり行かせてください
Since it's the last one, let Matsuri go.

957
00:51:32,927 --> 00:51:34,627
まつり先輩、行くぞー！
Matsuri-senpai, let's go!

958
00:51:34,627 --> 00:51:37,927
3, 2, 1, Go!

959
00:51:37,927 --> 00:51:38,927
Start!

960
00:51:39,927 --> 00:51:41,427
うま！うま！
Good! Good!

961
00:51:55,427 --> 00:51:57,427
2個の時点で
At the point of two...

962
00:52:02,927 --> 00:52:04,927
どんどん時間が過ぎてって...
Time is passing so quickly...

963
00:52:08,927 --> 00:52:10,427
Time's up!

964
00:52:13,227 --> 00:52:14,927
くそー、2個かー
Damn, only two?

965
00:52:25,427 --> 00:52:27,427
一定集中で！
Focus on one spot!

966
00:52:29,927 --> 00:52:32,427
アドバイスを活かしてやろうかね
Shall I put the advice to use?

967
00:52:33,427 --> 00:52:36,427
トワ様の挑戦！3, 2, 1, Go!
Towa-sama's challenge! 3, 2, 1, Go!

968
00:52:36,427 --> 00:52:37,427
Start!

969
00:52:41,927 --> 00:52:43,927
惜しい！惜しい！
Close! So close!

970
00:52:57,427 --> 00:52:59,427
あと10秒！頑張れ！
10 seconds left! Good luck!

971
00:53:07,927 --> 00:53:09,427
Time's up!

972
00:53:10,927 --> 00:53:12,927
え、これくそむずじゃん
Eh, this is damn hard.

973
00:53:22,427 --> 00:53:23,927
Level 3

974
